ACTIONS Selenium

--> Hover over --> WebElements that will be displayed when hover on certain element wont be visible

==> Action class -> moveToElement() -> takes WebElement type
Mouse events:

- Double click
- Hover
- Drag and drop(when moving one object and droping inside other)
- Context click(right click)
- Move

Keyboard events:

Syntax
Actions name = new Actions(driver);
name.doubleClick();
name.doubleClick().perform();

